{"tid":2140019,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光舊菜：學生記者係假記者","createTime":"2020-08-04T16:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T10:51:40.000Z","uid":241748,"like":17,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2810201e3fc6fac6ecc764bdd98a6173d622ab51","tid":2140019,"uid":241748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"【科大編委就校方拒絕保障校媒記者之聲明】<br />\n<br />\n上月21日，本報派出的兩名前線記者於元朗YOHO商場採訪期間，遭警方以限聚令票控。<br />\n<br />\n本報早前去信學務長辦公室凌麗容女士，希望校方發出採訪工作證明，助本報記者上庭抗辯。不出所料，學務長辦公室以校方政策限制為由，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"red\">拒絕證明本報記者當時正在採訪</span></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n凌女士秉持一貫作風，指本報記者為「自發的公民記者」，警方不會承認。她更要求本報重新審核出外採訪的風險，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>停止鼓勵學生記者像「真記者」般採訪衝突現場</strong> (act as if they are real reporters)。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本報閱畢凌女士回函，除了遺憾，只有寒心。<br />\n<br />\n香港沒有記者發牌制度，基本法保障香港新聞自由，所有學媒、網媒一樣可行使採訪權，並不存在「假記者」一說。<br />\n<br />\n本報向校方要求工作證明的緣由，是作為上庭抗辯的證據；而凌女士不僅藉政策作擋箭牌，更試圖引述警方不承認學生記者的說法，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>暗指本報記者為「假記者」</strong></span></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n凌女士嘗試以警方的說法，去為記者下定義，即使法例並無列明何謂「假記者」；這意味著，凌女士代校方承認，警方就是法律。<br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖，早已蓋過紅色日晷。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n//凌麗容女士事蹟節錄：<br />\n<br />\n&middot;去年九月，閉門召見時任科大編委總編，<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">要求科大編委「小心謹慎」</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;去年十二月，本報記者出外採訪時被警員非禮，向凌求助。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">凌在交談中表現輕蔑，本報代表表示不滿，她更於道歉時竊笑</span></span>，對女記者造成二次傷害。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;上篇報導中「被和解」的LG1淋奶茶事件，亦是由凌麗容女士跟進。<br />\n<br />\n科大編委 小心謹慎<br />\n<br />\n原po傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDeGBptBvuR/?igshid=qncgd6f91mhw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDeGBptBvuR%2F%3Figshid%3Dqncgd6f91mhw&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeaqEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=7caef539\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDeGBptBvuR%2F%3Figshid%3Dqncgd6f91mhw&h=8884691a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CDeGBptBvuR/?igshid=qncgd6f91mhw</a>"},{"pid":"d11ee9de68c420599637cbca08fff63dc48198c4","tid":2140019,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T18:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d298e7a269b988ca192ac7c6b17738b0f8ee61","tid":2140019,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T18:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a9d22b5ee3e394cff066cafb08e887ef43a502","tid":2140019,"uid":88743,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T18:51:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HHOKej2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHHOKej2.png&h=33b831e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f20ac7e747416475a94db575dc91f513a4595c3","tid":2140019,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:34:17.000Z","msg":"條友係咪想申請制裁"},{"pid":"38bd1d332c05348e50f21c1e3a0f5059d0b13b32","tid":2140019,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:56:59.000Z","msg":"佢老母就假"},{"pid":"e13a73751c41f54099cfe3f5e58038314fc522f9","tid":2140019,"uid":362015,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T22:58:19.000Z","msg":"香港班so call精英<br />\n十居其九都係大仆街"},{"pid":"2ba2460e545b75eab910d3630f8a3dbf11da3a8a","tid":2140019,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T23:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces